gdlex-ocr (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * First release of the Fascicoli PDP/TIAP line.
  * Add local casefile folder analysis through:
    --analyze-casefile INPUT_DIR --output OUTPUT_DIR.
  * Generate privacy-safe fascicolo_index.json and fascicolo_index.md outputs.
  * Scan folders locally without OCR and without reading PDF contents, using
    filenames, SHA-256 hashes, and lightweight indexes.
  * Add duplicate warnings, filename-based document classification, lightweight
    TXT/CSV/HTML/XML index detection and parsing, and index-document matching.
  * Harden pre-release audit edge cases: empty filenames, path traversal, and
    XML parsing through defusedxml.
  * Expand synthetic offline tests to 418.

