gdlex-ocr (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * First release of the Sentenze / Impugnazioni line.
  * Add offline Markdown judgment parser and CLI:
    --analyze-judgment INPUT.md --output OUTPUT.
  * Add --prepend to write the judgment card before the Markdown output while
    preserving the input file.
  * Add post-conversion PDF integration through
    --analyze-judgment-after-conversion, writing sentenza_analysis.md next to
    the main Markdown without modifying it.
  * Record privacy-safe judgment_analysis metadata in manifest.json.
  * Add the GUI checkbox "Analisi sentenza per impugnazione".
  * Harden judgment parsing for court authority, limitation periods, plea
    bargaining, acquittal formulas, and deadlines written in words.
  * Expand synthetic offline tests for CLI, PDF flow, GUI, manifest, and parser
    edge cases.

